+/// One layer of a DIT butterfly network (layer=1) where all blocks within a parallel submat
+/// share the same pair of two twiddle factors.
+///
+/// At layer=1 in `first_half_general`, `half_block_size=2`, `block_size=4`. Within each parallel
+/// submat, all blocks reuse the same two twiddles: the first row-pair of each block uses `t0`
