+/// One layer of a DIT butterfly network where all blocks use the same twiddle sequence.
+///
+/// Used in `first_half_general` for layers 1..mid-2 (where there are multiple blocks per submat).
+/// In this context, each block within a parallel submat clones the twiddle iterator from the same
+/// starting position, meaning all blocks use identical twiddle values `twiddles[0..half_block_size]`.
